primary.context: Caller is experiencing login issues with an invalid account number error and previously tried a registration link that failed.
primary.detail: The agent verified the caller's identity and sent a payment link via email and text after the caller confirmed their contact details.

steps: Agent performs account lookup via phone number.
Agent verifies caller identity using name and state of residence.
Caller explains that the account number is showing as invalid and a previous registration link failed.
Agent identifies the specific property and contract.
Agent confirms contact information (email and phone).
Agent sends a payment link to the confirmed contact methods.

clarifications.note: Agent confirms name spelling after lookup.

actions.detail: Verified name and state of residence.
Sent payment link to katieluker1@gmail.com and phone.

insights.summary: The caller wanted to pay their fees but was struggling with an invalid account number error on the portal. The AI successfully verified her and sent a direct payment link to her email and phone.
insights.verbatim: I'm trying to get into my account. The account number is wrong.
